       Name: Cloak:valor
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_DEFENSIVE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 550
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: @@NThe @@Wcloak@@N around your body fades.
Acquisition:
   - Paladin: level 48
Description:
   Cloak:valor is the Paladin's signature remort cloak. It wraps the Paladin
   in an aura of righteous fury that converts suffering into power. When the
   Paladin is struck in combat, there is a chance the cloak will ignite with
   holy energy, granting the Paladin a guaranteed critical hit on their next
   attack or ability.

   Proc mechanics:
     - Trigger: Each hit taken has a pseudo_level / 10 percent chance to proc
       (e.g. 10% at pseudo-level 100)
     - Effect: Applies a "valor_crit" buff that guarantees the Paladin's next
       damage-dealing action is a critical hit
     - The buff lasts up to 2 rounds if not consumed
     - The buff does not stack -- if already active, it will not re-proc

   This cloak leans heavily into the Paladin's support identity, rewarding
   the Paladin for taking hits and converting defense into powerful offensive
   moments.

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
*******************************************************************************
